'''Mesothelioma''' is a cancer that hits the lungs. It has many possible causes, in particular [[asbestos]]. This cancer can be deadly. It is different from [[asbestosis]], another disease caused by asbestos. Mesothelioma has been the subject of many [[lawsuit]]s, and many [[lawyer]]s specialize in mesothelioma and asbestosis.

